    <p>Traditional game theory:</p>
    <p>player pi selects strategy ai =&gt; strategy profile a</p>
    <p>actual cost for player pi : costa(i,a)</p>
    <p>Friendly game theory:</p>
    <p>consider cost of friends : F 2 [0,1] Friendship Factor</p>
    <p>perceived cost cp(i,a) = ca(i,a) + F  ca(j,a)</p>
    <p>New model: care about your friends wellbeing</p>
    <p>neighbour pj</p>
    <p>new equilibria (FNE)</p>
    <p>Windfall of Friendship WoF(F) = cost(aworstNE)</p>
    <p>cost(aworstFNE)</p>
    <p>____________</p>
  </div>
